prompt:
Extract all `interface def` declarations from this SysML v2 model.

Return a JSON array where each object contains:
- "name": the interface definition name
- "ends": array of {"name": end name, "type": port type, "conjugate": true/false if prefixed with ~}

Example output format:
```json
[
  {
    "name": "VerbalCommunication",
    "ends": [
      {"name": "communicationPartnerA", "type": "VerbalExchange", "conjugate": false},
      {"name": "communicationPartnerB", "type": "VerbalExchange", "conjugate": true}
    ]
  }
]
```

Also extract interface usages (interface statements with connect clauses) if present.
